name: ClipVest Twilight
name_cn: 回形针上装 暮光色
description:
Stegman's ClipVest is a multi-purpose work harness that keeps your tools handy when and where you need them. Built from industrial strength materials, this harness offers a back piece to help alleviate strain and provide counterbalance.
Women's sizes currently out of stock.
description_cn:
施特格曼的回形针上装是一款多功能的工作马甲,它让你的工具时刻方便取用.此马甲采用工业级高强度材料制成,可提供后背支撑以减轻压力并提供平衡力.
女款目前缺货.
